20.4 Handling Isotopes 
 

 
The OEChem library also provides two functions for dealing with
specific isotopes.  Both functions take an unsigned integer
representing the isotope's atomic number (number of protons), and an
unsigned integer representing the isotope's mass (number of protons
plus neutrons).

  

